  "title": "Muscles of the arm",
  "body_html": "Remember for the exam you need to know the action and innervation of the following anterior arm muscles only:<br /> <br /><ul><li>Coracobrachialis</li><li>Brachialis</li><li>Biceps Brachii</li></ul><br />Knowledge of origins and insertions is not required. All of the above are innervated by the musculocutaneous nerve (brachialis also has innervation from the radial nerve)<br /><br /><i>Diagram illustrating position of Brachialis & Coracobrachialis</i><br /><br /><CENTER><table><tr><td align = 'left' colspan='2'><a data-fancybox class='fancybox' rel='group' href='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/images_MRCEMnotes/swb012b.jpg'><img class='ajaximage' src='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/images_MRCEMnotes/swb012.jpg'/></a></td></tr><tr><td valign='top' align='left'> <span style = 'font-size:11px; color:LightGray;'>Image sourced from </span><a href='http://www.therapycouch.com/AP.Muscles.Arm.htm'  target='_blank' style = 'font-size:11px; color:LightGray;' >Wikipedia</a></td><td align='right'><a data-fancybox class='fancybox lbmagglasslink' rel='group' href='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/images_MRCEMnotes/swb012b.jpg'><img src='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/css/images/mag_glass.png'/></a></td></tr></table></CENTER><br /><i>Diagram illustrating position of Biceps</i><br /><br /><CENTER><table><tr><td align = 'left' colspan='2'><a data-fancybox class='fancybox' rel='group' href='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/images_MRCEMnotes/swb013b.jpg'><img class='ajaximage' src='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/images_MRCEMnotes/swb013.jpg'/></a></td></tr><tr><td valign='top' align='left'> <span style = 'font-size:11px; color:LightGray;'>Image sourced from </span><a href='http://classconnection.s3.amazonaws.com/183/flashcards/879183/jpg/bicepsbrachii1323682800033.jpg'  target='_blank' style = 'font-size:11px; color:LightGray;' >Wikipedia</a></td><td align='right'><a data-fancybox class='fancybox lbmagglasslink' rel='group' href='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/images_MRCEMnotes/swb013b.jpg'><img src='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/css/images/mag_glass.png'/></a></td></tr></table></CENTER></div>\n\n<div id=\"mybodylinks\"></div>\n\n<div id=\"mybodymedia\"></div>\n\n\n<div id=\"categorynum\">1</div>\n\n<div id=\"subcategorynum\">6</div>\n\n<div id=\"categoryname\">Anatomy</div>\n\n<div id=\"subcategoryname\">Upper limb anatomy</div>\n<div id=\"mybody\">\n\n<div id=\"body_content\">\nRemember for the exam you need to know the action and innervation of the following anterior arm muscles only:<br /> <br /><ul><li>Coracobrachialis</li><li>Brachialis</li><li>Biceps Brachii</li></ul><br />Knowledge of origins and insertions is not required. All of the above are innervated by the musculocutaneous nerve (brachialis also has innervation from the radial nerve)<br /><br /><i>Diagram illustrating position of Brachialis & Coracobrachialis</i><br /><br /><CENTER><table><tr><td align = 'left' colspan='2'><a data-fancybox class='fancybox' rel='group' href='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/images_MRCEMnotes/swb012b.jpg'><img class='ajaximage' src='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/images_MRCEMnotes/swb012.jpg'/></a></td></tr><tr><td valign='top' align='left'> <span style = 'font-size:11px; color:LightGray;'>Image sourced from </span><a href='http://www.therapycouch.com/AP.Muscles.Arm.htm'  target='_blank' style = 'font-size:11px; color:LightGray;' >Wikipedia</a></td><td align='right'><a data-fancybox class='fancybox lbmagglasslink' rel='group' href='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/images_MRCEMnotes/swb012b.jpg'><img src='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/css/images/mag_glass.png'/></a></td></tr></table></CENTER><br /><i>Diagram illustrating position of Biceps</i><br /><br /><CENTER><table><tr><td align = 'left' colspan='2'><a data-fancybox class='fancybox' rel='group' href='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/images_MRCEMnotes/swb013b.jpg'><img class='ajaximage' src='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/images_MRCEMnotes/swb013.jpg'/></a></td></tr><tr><td valign='top' align='left'> <span style = 'font-size:11px; color:LightGray;'>Image sourced from </span><a href='http://classconnection.s3.amazonaws.com/183/flashcards/879183/jpg/bicepsbrachii1323682800033.jpg'  target='_blank' style = 'font-size:11px; color:LightGray;' >Wikipedia</a></td><td align='right'><a data-fancybox class='fancybox lbmagglasslink' rel='group' href='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/images_MRCEMnotes/swb013b.jpg'><img src='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/css/images/mag_glass.png'/></a></td></tr></table></CENTER></div>\n\n\n<BR><BR><br><br>",
